<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<% const PAGE = 'rule'; %>

<head>
    <%- include('includes/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/prism-themes@1.3.0/themes/prism-vs.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/codemirror@5.49.2/lib/codemirror.css">
    <style>
        .CodeMirror {
            height: 45rem;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body class="sk-bg-gray">
    <%- include('includes/github-corner') %>
    <%- include('includes/navbar') %>
    <div class="container sk-my-8">
        <%- include('includes/steps', { PAGE }) %>
        <div class="card sk-center">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h4 text-center sk-mb-4">Rule 配置</h2>
                <div class="text-justify ce-card-docs">
                    <p>在这里，您需要填充 Clash 的规则部分配置。注意规则配置第一行必须为 <code>rules:</code>。</p>
                    <p>Clash 可以通过域名（<code>DOMAIN-SUFFIX</code> <code>DOMAIN-KEYWORD</code> <code>DOMAIN</code>）、目标 IP（<code>IP-CIDR</code>）、来源 IP（<code>SRC-IP-CIDR</code>）、目标端口（<code>DST-PORT</code>）、来源端口（<code>SRC-PORT</code>）和目标国家（<code>GEOIP</code>）匹配请求，具体如何使用请参考下面提供的样例。</p>
                    <br>
                    <pre><code class="language-yaml"><%- include('includes/sample/rule.yaml') %></code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card sk-center sk-mt-4">
            <div class="card-body ce-card-docs">
                <p>上一步您创建了以下策略组：<span id="rule-proxygroup-list"></span>。</p>
                <p class="sk-mb-0">您在接下来编写规则组时只能使用这些策略组和 <code>DIRECT</code>，<code>REJECT</code>。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card sk-center sk-mt-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card" id="rule-editor"></div>
                <br>
                <p id="msg">在继续下一步之前，必须先点击「检查」按钮</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                <div class="text-right">
                    <button id="ce-rule-btn-validate" class="btn btn-success sk-px-4">检查</button>
                    <a id="ce-rule-btn-continue" href="#" data-href="/finish" class="btn btn-primary sk-px-4 disabled" disabled>结束</a>
                    <a href="/proxygroup" class="btn btn-dark sk-px-4">返回</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('includes/modal') %>
    <%- include('includes/footer') %>
    <%- include('includes/footer_for_editor') %>
    <script src="/js/<%= PAGE %>.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
